:*XXIV Panzer Corps (Geyr von Schweppenburg) 
::3rd Pz, 4th Pz, 10th Mot.Div. 
:*XLVII Panzer Corps (Lemelsen) 
::17th Pz, 18th Pz, 29th Mot.Div.

*4th Army (von Kluge) 
:*VII Army Corps (Fahrmbacher) 
