== Business notebooks ==

=== HP OmniBook ===

HP&#x27;s line of business-oriented notebook computers since 1993. In chronological order of release:

Following HP&#x27;s acquisition of Compaq in 2002, this series of notebooks was discontinued, replaced with the HP Pavilion, HP Compaq, and Compaq Presario notebooks.

The OmniBook name would later be repurposed for a line of consumer-oriented notebooks in 2024, made to complement (and supersede) the Pavilion and Spectre series of notebooks.

===Compaq Evo===

The Compaq Evo line of business desktops and laptops were originally made by Compaq and was rebranded HP Compaq after the 2002 merger (see below for recent products).

