*HP NetServer LH4 (retired)
*HP NetServer LH4R (retired)
*HP NetServer LH3000 (retired)
*HP NetServer LH6000 (retired)
*HP NetServer LHX8000 (retired)
*HP NetServer LHX8500 (retired)

